"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-09-10-rebecca-cheptegeis-ex-boyfriend-dies-in-hospital-after-burning-olympic-athlete-alive\", \"text\": \"Published  on  By  Man who allegedly set his girlfriend Rebecca Cheptegei on fire, Dickson Ndiema is dead.  Ndiema, died on Monday from burns sustained during the attack on the Ugandan athlete.  DAILY POST recalls that Ndiema had doused Cheptegei in petrol and set her ablaze while she was returning to her house from church in western Trans Nzoia County, Nairobi, on September 1.  The 33-year-old athlete suffered burns covering 75 percent of her body and was being treated at the Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital in Eldoret City.  However, the attack affected several organs in her body which ultimatelyled to her death.    LaLiga: Real Madrid surprised Mbappe 'totally different' from Cristiano Ronaldo  Super Eagles: Labbadia walking out on NFF very embarrassing - Sports Minister, Enoh  Ugandan athlete Rebecca Cheptegei dies after boyfriend set her ablaze  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\"}"